TRNParser - Class in files
A parser for different formats of TRN information to GML format Currently there's available: - SIF (Single Input File) format (STILL IN DEVELOPMENT) - SynTReN format Final GML format has the following keys: d0 - "node" - "name" - string - node name d1 - "node" - "type" - string - node type d2 - "edge" - "type" - ac|re|du - ac for activator, re for repressor and du for dual
